The code in this repository (the researcher's instruction files and the
docs/index.html landing page) is MIT-licensed and free to study and reuse.

NOTE ON DOMAIN CONTENT: The evidence scaffolding cites public, peer-reviewed
research (Wilke 2016, Langevin & Yandow 2002) and publicly published
frameworks (Thomas Myers' Anatomy Trains, Bob Cooley's meridian circuits).
Those sources retain their own authors' rights. The Thai Sen-line material is
presented as transmitted lineage tradition; the lineage source is credited,
not claimed. The flash-card decks and books linked from this repo are
commercial products of Gabe Yoga and are NOT MIT-licensed — only the sampler
depth referenced here is free.
